User Input:

India successfully launched a new communication satellite from the Satish Dhawan Space Centre. ISRO scientists confirmed that the mission achieved all planned objectives.

System Process:

•User enters the news.
•Flask backend receives the text.
•Text is cleaned and converted using TF-IDF.
•The trained Passive Aggressive Classifier             analyzes the text.
•The model predicts the result.

Output:

Prediction: Real News ✅
Confidence: 98.2%